00:13:07,600 --> 00:13:09,400
This is Officer Wu
from the police station.

278
00:13:09,840 --> 00:13:10,680
Nice to meet you.

279
00:13:10,720 --> 00:13:12,600
Wu, this is Bi Zhigang from

280
00:13:12,600 --> 00:13:13,440
the secretary's office.

281
00:13:14,000 --> 00:13:15,980
(Bi Zhigang, Factory Secretary)
Come have tea with me sometime.

282
00:13:16,520 --> 00:13:17,360
So, what's the situation?

283
00:13:17,400 --> 00:13:18,320
We're interrogating,

284
00:13:18,600 --> 00:13:20,600
but they all deny
throwing the first punch.

285
00:13:22,080 --> 00:13:22,920
We hold disciplinary

286
00:13:23,160 --> 00:13:25,680
and ideological education sessions
every month.

287
00:13:26,160 --> 00:13:28,160
Our workers are civilized and rule-abiding.

288
00:13:28,600 --> 00:13:29,760
They wouldn't

289
00:13:31,440 --> 00:13:32,840
start fights, right?

290
00:13:32,840 --> 00:13:34,440
That's right.

291
00:13:39,040 --> 00:13:40,880
You are Lu Dajiang's cousin, right?

292
00:13:41,640 --> 00:13:43,920
Your cousin used to dominate Fucheng.

293
00:13:44,240 --> 00:13:45,720
How come you're so worthless?

294
00:13:46,000 --> 00:13:47,640
Getting beaten down like this.

295
00:13:48,080 --> 00:13:49,080
Hey, Bi...

296
00:13:54,680 --> 00:13:56,360
- What are you doing?
- I may not have my brother's power,

297
00:13:56,360 --> 00:13:57,680
but I can swat flies,

298
00:13:57,680 --> 00:13:59,560
especially annoying ones like you.

299
00:13:59,840 --> 00:14:00,960
- I...
- Dude,

300
00:14:01,440 --> 00:14:02,650
haven't washed your hair in years, huh?

301
00:14:02,840 --> 00:14:04,040
Your mousse is probably stinking.

302
00:14:05,800 --> 00:14:07,560
Look, it must have been him
who threw the first punch.

303
00:14:07,560 --> 00:14:08,490
Arrest him! It's definitely him.

304
00:14:08,500 --> 00:14:09,240
- It must be him!
- Alright!

305
00:14:09,240 --> 00:14:10,280
Calm down.

306
00:14:11,960 --> 00:14:13,120
(Security Department)

307
00:14:13,200 --> 00:14:14,320
- Captain Wu.
- Get down.

308
00:14:14,320 --> 00:14:15,960
She said she saw
who threw the first punch.

309
00:14:17,680 --> 00:14:19,520
Who was it?

310
00:14:25,160 --> 00:14:26,840
- Him.
- I told you!

311
00:14:26,840 --> 00:14:28,320
Dong, take him with us.

312
00:14:28,400 --> 00:14:29,480
Everyone else can go.

313
00:14:29,480 --> 00:14:31,080
- Let's go.
- Have a good day.

314
00:14:31,080 --> 00:14:32,040
You've got the wrong person.

315
00:14:32,400 --> 00:14:33,240
Shut up!

316
00:14:33,360 --> 00:14:34,280
None of your business!

317
00:14:34,880 --> 00:14:35,760
Get lost!

318
00:14:37,080 --> 00:14:38,000
This is not over.

319
00:14:38,640 --> 00:14:39,480
Of course it is not,

320
00:14:39,880 --> 00:14:41,080
you owe me a suitcase.

321
00:14:52,760 --> 00:14:53,600
Xiaolu,

322
00:14:54,240 --> 00:14:57,110
I think you can still make it to the exam.

323
00:14:57,120 --> 00:14:58,560
There's a shortcut
by the vegetable market.

324
00:14:58,560 --> 00:14:59,800
Hurry on your bike, you can get there.

325
00:15:00,120 --> 00:15:01,680
- Just go.
- Thanks, Uncle Wu.

326
00:15:03,720 --> 00:15:05,320
- I'm going.
- Good luck!

327
00:15:05,600 --> 00:15:06,800
Strive to become a college student.

328
00:15:06,920 --> 00:15:08,040
- Don't be like your cousin.
- Okay.

329
00:15:09,280 --> 00:15:10,240
That's it?

330
00:15:11,640 --> 00:15:12,920
We've taken him out of the factory.

331
00:15:12,920 --> 00:15:14,480
Will you buy him lunch if we keep him?

332
00:15:15,240 --> 00:15:16,080
Let's go back.

333
00:15:22,760 --> 00:15:23,600
Honey,

334
00:15:24,040 --> 00:15:25,800
when did you start believing in this?

335
00:15:27,280 --> 00:15:29,280
Li Guangnan's mother taught me this.

336
00:15:29,600 --> 00:15:32,600
She said the students would be blessed.

337
00:15:32,720 --> 00:15:34,160
Didn't you say that

338
00:15:34,280 --> 00:15:35,840
our son is naturally bright,

339
00:15:35,960 --> 00:15:37,760
born to excel in academics?

340
00:15:38,120 --> 00:15:39,520
I didn't tell the truth

341
00:15:39,520 --> 00:15:41,000
in front of him just now.

342
00:15:41,160 --> 00:15:42,840
Actually, the teachers said,

343
00:15:42,960 --> 00:15:44,320
"Your son, Lu Xiaolu,

344
00:15:44,320 --> 00:15:45,360
is intelligent enough

345
00:15:45,360 --> 00:15:46,760
for college,

346
00:15:46,760 --> 00:15:49,160
but he's mischievous and doesn't study hard.

347
00:15:49,160 --> 00:15:51,480
It's difficult for him to even get
into the top ten in the class."

348
00:15:51,840 --> 00:15:52,700
Mischievous and lazy,

349
00:15:52,740 --> 00:15:54,080
yet he can still make it into the top ten.

350
00:15:54,080 --> 00:15:55,200
What kind of intelligence is this?

351
00:15:55,600 --> 00:15:56,620
Whose intelligence did he get?

352
00:15:56,880 --> 00:15:57,800
Apparently yours, isn't it?

353
00:15:59,440 --> 00:16:01,160
Not at all.

354
00:16:01,520 --> 00:16:02,880
When I was a student,

355
00:16:03,120 --> 00:16:05,120
I was always in the top three of the class.

356
00:16:05,560 --> 00:16:06,960
I was good-looking,

357
00:16:06,960 --> 00:16:08,320
and my grades were decent.

358
00:16:08,520 --> 00:16:10,440
Every teacher liked me.

359
00:16:11,400 --> 00:16:12,800
- Let me tell you.
- What?

360
00:16:13,720 --> 00:16:14,920
Many people

361
00:16:15,160 --> 00:16:16,680
in our factory ask for

362
00:16:16,800 --> 00:16:18,600
a celebratory banquet when they see me.

363
00:16:19,160 --> 00:16:20,400
I've booked a restaurant.

364
00:16:20,920 --> 00:16:23,360
If this brat doesn't do well,

365
00:16:23,640 --> 00:16:24,960
what will we do?

366
00:16:25,160 --> 00:16:26,440
He'll definitely do well.

367
00:16:26,440 --> 00:16:27,480
No problem.

368
00:16:37,640 --> 00:16:41,280
(Brave the waves, pass with flying colors)

369
00:16:47,600 --> 00:16:48,880
Sir, please don't lock the door.

370
00:16:48,880 --> 00:16:49,840
Let me in.

371
00:16:50,120 --> 00:16:51,560
Stop yelling.
They're taking exams inside.

372
00:16:51,560 --> 00:16:52,720
I'm here to take the exam too.

373
00:16:52,720 --> 00:16:53,960
- Let me in.
- I can't.

374
00:16:55,800 --> 00:16:56,640
Mr. Zhang!

375
00:16:57,000 --> 00:16:57,840
Mr. Zhang!

376
00:16:57,920 --> 00:16:58,840
Please don't shout.

377
00:16:59,200 --> 00:17:00,040
Mr. Hu!

378
00:17:00,200 --> 00:17:01,080
Please let me in!

379
00:17:01,080 --> 00:17:02,480
- I'm Xiaolu!
- Young man,

380
00:17:02,600 --> 00:17:04,000
if you shout again, I'll call the police.

381
00:17:04,000 --> 00:17:05,800
Please, sir, please let me in.

382
00:17:10,360 --> 00:17:11,560
Why are you also outside?

383
00:17:12,160 --> 00:17:13,560
We were both in the fight this morning,

384
00:17:13,800 --> 00:17:15,320
how can I go in alone?

385
00:17:20,840 --> 00:17:21,960
My brother.

386
00:17:22,880 --> 00:17:23,720
Take this.

387
00:17:39,560 --> 00:17:40,560
(Parents, please keep out)

388
00:17:40,560 --> 00:17:41,520
How will you explain

389
00:17:41,840 --> 00:17:43,000
to your mom tonight?

390
00:17:43,720 --> 00:17:44,560
Explain?

391
00:17:44,960 --> 00:17:45,880
Dare I say anything?

392
00:17:49,960 --> 00:17:50,800
The problem is,

393
00:17:50,800 --> 00:17:52,840
even if I go to take the exam,

394
00:17:53,640 --> 00:17:55,120
I might not pass.

395
00:17:55,920 --> 00:17:56,760
But you could

396
00:17:57,640 --> 00:17:59,360
at least pass a vocational school.

397
00:18:00,680 --> 00:18:01,520
I'm sorry.

398
00:18:01,960 --> 00:18:03,800
It's all because of me.

399
00:18:05,840 --> 00:18:06,880
No big deal.

400
00:18:07,360 --> 00:18:08,520
It's just the college entrance exam.

401
00:18:08,960 --> 00:18:10,760
With my intelligence and talent,

402
00:18:11,160 --> 00:18:12,320
even if I don't go to college,

403
00:18:12,520 --> 00:18:13,480
I can do anything.

404
00:18:24,360 --> 00:18:25,640
Maybe we can work in a factory.

405
00:18:26,280 --> 00:18:27,200
In a factory?

406
00:18:27,200 --> 00:18:28,040
Yeah.

407
00:18:28,840 --> 00:18:30,080
Working in a factory is honorable,

408
00:18:30,600 --> 00:18:31,920
especially if you can

409
00:18:31,920 --> 00:18:33,000
get into that food factory.

410
00:18:33,400 --> 00:18:34,560
Not only is the welfare good,

411
00:18:34,880 --> 00:18:37,320
with endless bread and soda every month,

412
00:18:38,440 --> 00:18:41,040
but more importantly, it's the factory
with the most girls in the city.

413
00:18:41,200 --> 00:18:42,280
Little Pouter works there too.

414
00:18:46,000 --> 00:18:47,560
Let's focus on surviving tonight now.

415
00:18:51,480 --> 00:18:52,320
Alright,

416
00:18:52,800 --> 00:18:53,800
stop sulking. It's no use.

417
00:18:54,000 --> 00:18:54,840
Come with me

418
00:18:55,800 --> 00:18:56,640
to find my cousin.

419
00:18:58,040 --> 00:18:59,520
My mom's waiting for me at home.

420
00:18:59,520 --> 00:19:01,120
It's too early to go back and meet death.

421
00:19:03,040 --> 00:19:04,400
Early death, early reincarnation.

