00:19:28,800 --> 00:19:30,840
Although he used to be
a worker in our factory,

426
00:19:31,520 --> 00:19:32,600
he committed some bad deeds

427
00:19:32,600 --> 00:19:33,840
and ran off to Hong Kong.

428
00:19:34,240 --> 00:19:35,120
Now he's a

429
00:19:35,120 --> 00:19:36,960
complete troublemaker.

430
00:19:37,720 --> 00:19:38,880
So what if he has money?

431
00:19:39,640 --> 00:19:42,080
We don't associate with such social scum.

432
00:19:44,320 --> 00:19:45,520
Anyway, don't give him the project.

433
00:19:47,880 --> 00:19:49,280
Just do as I say.

434
00:19:52,520 --> 00:19:53,880
He can talk to me at the factory!

435
00:19:55,200 --> 00:19:56,040
He's on his way?

436
00:19:56,040 --> 00:19:57,680
(Lu Dajiang, Domineering Man of Fucheng)

437
00:19:58,920 --> 00:20:00,040
Why didn't you say this earlier?

438
00:20:00,960 --> 00:20:01,800
Director,

439
00:20:01,920 --> 00:20:03,000
this is Bai Lan,

440
00:20:03,000 --> 00:20:04,520
our new factory doctor.

441
00:20:05,280 --> 00:20:07,000
I just graduated from university,

442
00:20:07,000 --> 00:20:08,400
and I brought her to meet with you.

443
00:20:14,080 --> 00:20:14,920
You...

444
00:20:15,680 --> 00:20:16,520
You are...

445
00:20:23,000 --> 00:20:23,920
Where is my cousin?

446
00:20:27,010 --> 00:20:27,880
Who's your cousin?

447
00:20:27,880 --> 00:20:28,920
Cut the crap!

448
00:20:30,680 --> 00:20:32,600
Someone told me you had him arrested.

449
00:20:33,440 --> 00:20:34,320
That's right,

450
00:20:35,000 --> 00:20:36,840
he openly harassed
one of our factory workers

451
00:20:36,920 --> 00:20:38,320
and got involved in a fight.

452
00:20:38,920 --> 00:20:40,120
The evidence is clear,

453
00:20:40,720 --> 00:20:41,840
and the witness is right here.

454
00:20:41,920 --> 00:20:43,120
He was just taken away by the police.

455
00:20:45,520 --> 00:20:47,480
Good for you, Bi Zhigang,

456
00:20:48,520 --> 00:20:50,280
now you're acting all dignified

457
00:20:51,000 --> 00:20:52,240
and you dare to touch my cousin.

458
00:20:52,240 --> 00:20:53,080
I...

459
00:20:53,560 --> 00:20:54,440
Don't forget

460
00:20:55,120 --> 00:20:56,360
how you begged me

461
00:20:56,840 --> 00:20:58,200
when I beat you up back then.

462
00:20:58,600 --> 00:20:59,760
I was a student cadre.

463
00:20:59,760 --> 00:21:01,320
I couldn't stoop to your level.

464
00:21:01,320 --> 00:21:02,160
You...

465
00:21:03,160 --> 00:21:04,040
Hey, you...

466
00:21:05,240 --> 00:21:07,240
What are you doing?
Don't be afraid. I'm here.

467
00:21:08,400 --> 00:21:09,560
You're the witness?

468
00:21:09,920 --> 00:21:10,920
What did you see?

469
00:21:12,160 --> 00:21:14,080
I don't know if your cousin
harassed the female worker,

470
00:21:14,640 --> 00:21:15,920
but he did hit someone

471
