472
00:21:17,760 --> 00:21:18,600
That's right.

473
00:21:20,800 --> 00:21:22,280
I'll pay you double for the suitcase.

474
00:21:23,360 --> 00:21:24,960
Call the police now

475
00:21:25,280 --> 00:21:26,320
