476
00:21:26,640 --> 00:21:27,920
Get him released right now.

477
00:21:28,560 --> 00:21:30,800
Lu Dajiang, stop messing around here!

478
00:21:31,000 --> 00:21:32,480
Just shut up.

479
00:21:32,480 --> 00:21:33,920
- Hey, you...
- He hit someone. That's the truth.

480
00:21:33,920 --> 00:21:35,360
I can't lie to the police.

481
00:21:35,640 --> 00:21:36,720
That's right.

482
00:21:44,560 --> 00:21:45,400
Pig Teeth,

483
00:21:45,400 --> 00:21:46,240
Dumb Jar,

484
00:21:47,680 --> 00:21:48,720
close the door.

485
00:21:50,190 --> 00:21:51,040
- You...
- What are you doing?

486
00:21:51,040 --> 00:21:52,360
You... You...

487
00:21:52,360 --> 00:21:54,080
- What do you want?
- In broad daylight, this is...

488
00:21:54,080 --> 00:21:55,560
- Stop making trouble!
- What do you want?

489
00:21:55,560 --> 00:21:56,840
If they don't release him today,

490
00:21:56,840 --> 00:21:58,000
no one will leave.

491
00:21:58,280 --> 00:21:59,360
- Wait.
- Listen,

492
00:21:59,520 --> 00:22:00,840
