go to the police and ask for him.

495
00:22:04,200 --> 00:22:05,160
That's right.

496
00:22:05,160 --> 00:22:06,600
If you have the guts, go ahead.

497
00:22:07,840 --> 00:22:09,120
You are talking about logic?

498
00:22:11,280 --> 00:22:12,960
I may only have
a middle school education,

499
00:22:13,080 --> 00:22:14,200
but I understand logic.

500
00:22:15,560 --> 00:22:16,720
You framed him,

501
00:22:17,520 --> 00:22:18,800
so the police arrested him.

502
00:22:19,720 --> 00:22:20,680
Change your tune,

503
00:22:21,480 --> 00:22:22,440
and they'll release him,

504
00:22:23,160 --> 00:22:24,000
right?

505
00:22:24,020 --> 00:22:25,400
This is not logic at all.

506
00:22:26,200 --> 00:22:27,480
This is unreasonable.

507
00:22:28,200 --> 00:22:29,040
Let me tell you,

508
00:22:29,040 --> 00:22:30,280
this is the factory director's office,

509
00:22:30,280 --> 00:22:31,280
not where you can act wild.

510
00:22:31,280 --> 00:22:32,320
- Get out of here.
- Hit him!

511
00:22:33,040 --> 00:22:33,920
Don't do that!

512
00:22:34,520 --> 00:22:35,360
Why are you doing this?

513
00:22:35,640 --> 00:22:36,600
Call the police now.

514
00:22:36,600 --> 00:22:38,320
Let him go. You let go first.

515
00:22:39,240 --> 00:22:40,520
Let go, it's dangerous.

516
00:22:40,520 --> 00:22:41,400
- Make the call, will you?
- You...

517
00:22:41,400 --> 00:22:42,840
- Fine, I'll make a call.
- Do it now.

518
00:22:42,840 --> 00:22:43,680
Stop wasting time.

519
00:22:46,480 --> 00:22:47,320
Police officer?

520
00:22:47,400 --> 00:22:48,880
- Dajiang!
- Boss!

521
00:22:48,880 --> 00:22:49,720
Oh dear.

522
00:22:50,120 --> 00:22:51,360
She hit him hard.

523
00:22:51,520 --> 00:22:52,360
You... You guys...

524
00:22:52,440 --> 00:22:53,640
Stop messing around.

525
00:22:55,600 --> 00:22:56,560
Are you okay?

526
00:22:57,800 --> 00:22:59,960
No... No...

527
00:23:02,800 --> 00:23:03,640
Boss.

528
00:23:26,760 --> 00:23:28,000
Quickly release him.

529
00:23:29,040 --> 00:23:29,960
If you don't,

530
00:23:30,160 --> 00:23:31,560
just wait and see.

531
00:23:34,120 --> 00:23:35,000
Let's go.

532
00:23:35,000 --> 00:23:36,000
Pig Teeth, open the door.

533
00:23:37,920 --> 00:23:38,800
This

534
00:23:38,920 --> 00:23:40,080
