537
00:23:45,600 --> 00:23:46,720
They're gone. They're gone.

538
00:23:46,720 --> 00:23:48,040
No need to come here.

539
00:23:49,120 --> 00:23:50,680
Hit him! Hit him!

540
00:23:51,360 --> 00:23:52,480
Hit him!

541
00:23:54,600 --> 00:23:55,640
Punch him! Punch!

