Boss Ma,

545
00:24:09,440 --> 00:24:11,160
please protect my big brother
and keep him safe.

546
00:24:11,160 --> 00:24:12,280
What happened to him?

547
00:24:12,720 --> 00:24:13,600
He was...

548
00:24:13,960 --> 00:24:15,600
He was attacked by a woman.

549
00:24:15,800 --> 00:24:17,280
That crazy woman!

550
00:24:17,600 --> 00:24:18,680
Who is she?

551
00:24:18,680 --> 00:24:20,080
She wore a blue floral dress,

552
00:24:20,080 --> 00:24:21,200
white shirt,

553
00:24:21,760 --> 00:24:22,840
big eyes,

554
00:24:23,760 --> 00:24:24,920
quite pretty,

555
00:24:26,760 --> 00:24:28,160
but she's too vicious.

556
00:24:28,760 --> 00:24:30,440
Dajiang was fine when he was there,

557
00:24:30,560 --> 00:24:31,860
